{
  "stem": "617.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But most of the time, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just rushing us through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then as we were-- as we were-- about the fifth day, as we were walking, the oberscharfuhrer stopped us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said that the SS soldiers, apparently, the way he put it, were going to shoot us all, because they had to leave, because the Russian army was approaching very fast, and they wouldn't want to fall prisoners.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't want to leave us, so they were going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the oberscharfuhrer said, I will take care of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember him putting on-- you know, with bullets, a whole-- and-- because otherwise, he wasn't carrying any guns, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he put that on, and he stopped us, and he was telling us, look, the SS soldiers are leaving.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're in my care now, and I will be taking care of you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because that's what he said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russian army is approaching, and we-- they-- they have to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't want to become prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were going to shoot-- he-- he said it right then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he said that he's going to take over, and we should behave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And did we have any choice?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What were you thinking?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I said, we weren't thinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you, because really, all the time I was in camp, from the first day on, we never menstruated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There must have been something put in our food that not to think and not to have anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all this time, I imagine-- because really, we couldn't think straight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just-- one thing we were thinking, there's going to come a day soon that we'll be freed.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
